*[[魚潭國家森林公園|魚潭國家森林公園]]（部分）

===大石頭臉===
米勒德縣內的帕範谷擁有數個古老的熔岩流和死火山，其中包括“黑岩”熔岩流。“黑岩”附近有一個岩石雕像，名為“大石頭臉”（Great Stone Face）。<ref> [http://content.lib.utah.edu/cdm/ref/collection/USHS_Class/id/20364 Great Stone Face]</ref>在適當的角度下觀看，[[約瑟·斯密|約瑟·斯密]]的臉容會出現在“大石頭臉”上。<ref>[http://www.utahoutdooractivities.com/greatstoneface.html The Great Stone Face - Millard County].</ref><ref>{{citation |url= http://www.deseretnews.com/article/705378124/Does-the-Great-Stone-Face-really-resemble-the-Prophet-Joseph.html?pg=all |title= Does the Great Stone Face really resemble the Prophet Joseph? |first= Lynn |last= Arave |date= 2010-05-09 |newspaper= Deseret News }}</ref>

